WEBVTT

00:01:36.560 --> 00:01:38.959
Since Censor of Zhongzhou, Chao Heng,

00:01:39.079 --> 00:01:40.920
refuses to do me this favor,

00:01:41.319 --> 00:01:42.280
then the charges against him

00:01:42.280 --> 00:01:43.480
can never be cleared.

00:01:44.560 --> 00:01:45.400
By law,

00:01:46.120 --> 00:01:48.200
it means execution of the entire family.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:07.239
Why are you being so honest?

00:02:10.719 --> 00:02:11.560
I just

00:02:12.039 --> 00:02:13.080
don't want to lie to you.

00:02:13.639 --> 00:02:14.240
Watch out!

00:02:25.319 --> 00:02:26.439
Ye Li.

00:02:29.039 --> 00:02:30.159
Can you take me to see it?

00:02:46.080 --> 00:02:47.919
You have been by the Manor Lord's side,

00:02:47.919 --> 00:02:50.560
lying in wait and plotting for so long.

00:02:51.520 --> 00:02:52.960
You don't know the secret code,

00:02:53.400 --> 00:02:55.319
you don't know the Thousand-Mechanism Treasure,

00:02:56.080 --> 00:02:58.479
and even the whereabouts of the Manor Lord's daughter,

00:02:58.680 --> 00:03:00.000
you don't know either.

00:03:00.479 --> 00:03:02.319
Do you think I believe that?

00:03:03.520 --> 00:03:05.599
I really don't know.

00:03:15.639 --> 00:03:17.039
Didn't I tell you to get some good sleep?

00:03:17.800 --> 00:03:18.560
I couldn't sleep.

00:03:19.240 --> 00:03:20.360
I didn't want to be alone.

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:27.639
For someone like me who practiced martial arts from childhood,

00:03:28.639 --> 00:03:30.400
I never thought I'd be in such a sorry state today.

00:03:31.240 --> 00:03:32.840
Aren't you a legal advocate?

00:03:33.360 --> 00:03:34.360
Why practice martial arts?

00:03:35.199 --> 00:03:36.840
To protect the person I wanted to protect.

00:03:38.840 --> 00:03:40.080
The person you wanted to protect,

00:03:40.680 --> 00:03:43.360
where is she now?

00:03:44.280 --> 00:03:45.719
Is she not with you?

00:03:46.479 --> 00:03:47.520
We got separated.

00:03:48.520 --> 00:03:49.919
Of the things I promised her,

00:03:50.639 --> 00:03:51.919
I haven't accomplished a single one.

00:03:53.520 --> 00:03:54.879
I said I'd give her a home,

00:03:55.919 --> 00:03:57.560
but I ended up losing her instead.

00:03:58.919 --> 00:04:00.840
I said I'd clear her family's name,

00:04:01.879 --> 00:04:03.639
but I haven't even seen the case files.

00:04:04.400 --> 00:04:06.280
Instead, I've been reduced to a prisoner,

00:04:07.840 --> 00:04:09.240
and nearly lost my head.

00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:12.280
It's just as well that she's gone.

00:04:13.639 --> 00:04:15.280
Otherwise, seeing me like this now,

00:04:16.360 --> 00:04:17.560
she would probably be very disappointed.

00:04:17.839 --> 00:04:18.600
How could she be?

00:04:23.720 --> 00:04:26.079
Zhao Yun... it really is you.

00:04:28.120 --> 00:04:29.759
The things you've always wanted to do for her,

00:04:30.800 --> 00:04:31.879
were not just empty words.

00:04:31.920 --> 00:04:33.000
You have been working hard at them.

00:04:34.360 --> 00:04:35.319
That is already remarkable.

00:04:44.279 --> 00:04:45.360
But what use is that?

00:04:47.199 --> 00:04:48.759
In the end, I accomplished nothing.

00:04:57.040 --> 00:04:57.480
Zhao Yun...

00:04:57.480 --> 00:04:59.000
It's good that Zhao Yun has a friend like you.

00:05:03.920 --> 00:05:05.079
I really envy her.

00:05:10.639 --> 00:05:12.279
"Only the moon in the spring courtyard is affectionate,"

00:05:13.879 --> 00:05:15.439
"still shining on falling flowers for the parted one."

00:05:18.360 --> 00:05:19.639
Perhaps Zhao Yun and I

00:05:21.519 --> 00:05:23.319
will never meet again in this life.

00:05:25.160 --> 00:05:26.480
If you do not wish to reveal yourself,

00:05:27.279 --> 00:05:28.560
then so be it.

00:05:33.079 --> 00:05:34.680
Worldly matters are heavy,

00:05:35.319 --> 00:05:36.639
but flowers are light.

00:05:40.040 --> 00:05:40.879
Master Ye,

00:05:42.199 --> 00:05:43.600
don't be trapped in the past.

00:05:44.199 --> 00:05:45.399
Look to the road ahead.

00:05:46.920 --> 00:05:48.279
No matter how good the past was,

00:05:49.160 --> 00:05:51.079
it is but flowers in a mirror, moon in the water.

00:05:59.639 --> 00:06:00.680
You just said...

00:06:01.680 --> 00:06:02.959
"Flowers in a mirror, moon in the water"?

00:06:04.800 --> 00:06:05.720
What's wrong?

00:06:07.079 --> 00:06:09.079
I might know the solution to the third riddle.

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:18.519
Ye Li hasn't come back all night.

00:06:19.319 --> 00:06:20.439
I wonder how he is.

00:06:27.199 --> 00:06:28.160
There are no lotuses in the Lotus Garden.

00:06:28.879 --> 00:06:30.600
Because the manor is surrounded by poisonous miasma,

00:06:31.040 --> 00:06:32.120
the Red River water is contaminated,

00:06:32.519 --> 00:06:33.759
so lotus seeds cannot sprout.

00:06:34.240 --> 00:06:35.800
To please his wife, the Manor Lord

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:36.959
made artificial lotuses

00:06:36.959 --> 00:06:37.759
and placed them in vats

00:06:38.120 --> 00:06:39.279
for her to admire throughout the seasons.

00:06:44.759 --> 00:06:45.879
Do you have a clue?

00:06:47.720 --> 00:06:48.680
Look inside this vat.

00:06:49.240 --> 00:06:50.360
How is it different from last time?

00:06:56.040 --> 00:06:56.839
This...

00:06:57.639 --> 00:06:59.439
it's just full of water.

00:07:01.920 --> 00:07:03.240
I was wondering before,

00:07:03.959 --> 00:07:05.560
"The heavenly court calls out the water immortal."

00:07:06.319 --> 00:07:08.240
What exactly does this phrase mean?

00:07:09.040 --> 00:07:11.360
"Yellow clouds turning waves" didn't reveal the full picture.

00:07:12.000 --> 00:07:14.199
Then I thought of a saying:

00:07:15.079 --> 00:07:16.519
"Yellow sky brings rain."

00:07:17.959 --> 00:07:20.040
Yellow sky brings rain?

00:07:22.079 --> 00:07:23.360
Before a summer storm,

00:07:24.519 --> 00:07:25.639
the clouds are filled with water,

00:07:26.680 --> 00:07:27.279
and the sky

00:07:28.120 --> 00:07:29.839
takes on a very deep yellow hue.

00:07:32.120 --> 00:07:33.720
Just like at twilight.

00:07:46.319 --> 00:07:48.399
Yellow clouds churn waves in the nine heavens

00:07:49.199 --> 00:07:51.120
To see such a magnificent sight,

00:07:51.560 --> 00:07:53.199
it must be a stormy summer day.

00:07:54.759 --> 00:07:56.199
Rain falls from the sky,

00:07:57.000 --> 00:07:59.519
so only the Heavenly Court can summon the Water Immortal.

00:08:01.600 --> 00:08:04.319
Then the immortal in "The Immortal Points the Way,"

00:08:04.759 --> 00:08:05.879
who does that refer to?

00:08:06.120 --> 00:08:07.000
Who lives in the water?

00:08:09.439 --> 00:08:10.279
Lotuses?

00:08:10.720 --> 00:08:11.920
Who rules the waters?

00:08:12.759 --> 00:08:13.480
The Dragon King.

00:08:18.680 --> 00:08:19.480
Look.

00:08:21.279 --> 00:08:22.279
Isn't this a dragon?

00:08:24.199 --> 00:08:25.480
So the Water Immortal

00:08:25.759 --> 00:08:26.720
doesn't refer to a narcissus,

00:08:26.720 --> 00:08:27.519
nor a lotus.

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:28.759
It's a dragon.

00:08:32.360 --> 00:08:34.240
This is a double-headed dragon pattern.

00:08:36.879 --> 00:08:39.080
In the manor, something similar to this dragon pattern,

00:08:40.320 --> 00:08:41.559
I've only seen in one place.

00:08:49.000 --> 00:08:51.080
So the third line actually points to...

00:09:01.600 --> 00:09:02.399
Si Niang.

00:09:07.720 --> 00:09:08.720
Xu Qingqing.

00:09:09.960 --> 00:09:10.759
She's dead.